[SPEAKER_01] E to je taj dio koji mi je malo još ostao volan.

765
00:53:54,739 --> 00:53:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] U cijeloj priči.

766
00:53:56,159 --> 00:54:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] I te radikalizacije koje smo svi nekako prošli bili.

767
00:54:00,099 --> 00:54:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] To mi se ne sviđa.

768
00:54:01,840 --> 00:54:04,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju se ta prviča s cijepivom svela,

769
00:54:04,260 --> 00:54:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] da ne znamo je li dobro ili nije, bar ja kao lajk,

770
00:54:08,480 --> 00:54:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali ima jedna ona opasnost neka.

771
00:54:11,940 --> 00:54:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Cijepiva se neka spašavala živote.

772
00:54:14,360 --> 00:54:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] I još uvijek spašavala, samo što ljudi nisu svjesni toga,

773
00:54:17,280 --> 00:54:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] jer živimo u prilično jedno mirno doba kako je.

774
00:54:21,059 --> 00:54:24,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vakni ih i za pet godina u SSSR-u u bivšem,

775
00:54:24,119 --> 00:54:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] kako je, imaš difteriju nazad.

776
00:54:25,659 --> 00:54:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo nije prijetnja, to je tako kako je.

777
00:54:27,519 --> 00:54:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] Takav je život, nažalost.

778
00:54:30,280 --> 00:54:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ima jedna stvar koja je, kako komunicirati?

779
00:54:34,739 --> 00:54:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, recimo, zarazit ćeš se.

780
00:54:38,460 --> 00:54:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] Jer i kad se cijepiš protiv ospica, dobit ćeš ih.

781
00:54:43,239 --> 00:54:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] Sam neće biti manifestno i neće biti zarazan drugima.

782
00:54:45,699 --> 00:54:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] Što ti je, imaš manje šanse umreti, točka.

783
00:54:51,260 --> 00:54:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] I to je jedina stvar, recimo, koja je.

784
00:54:55,199 --> 00:54:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sve druge nadogradnje guše ljude.

785
00:54:59,380 --> 00:55:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] Reci samo to, a ti bire kako je.

786
00:55:02,119 --> 00:55:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] Nekako velim, ne bih potezao,

787
00:55:06,139 --> 00:55:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] smatram da je to sad pripada već zaista prošlosti,

788
00:55:08,639 --> 00:55:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] koja je, ja bih prije zvukao u sociološku komponentu,

789
00:55:12,039 --> 00:55:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] zašto se sve sve zbiva.

790
00:55:13,239 --> 00:55:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ako su ljudi ogorčeni, na koga su doista ogorčeni?

791
00:55:18,579 --> 00:55:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moraju sami se sobom raščistiti, moje mišljenje.

792
00:55:22,079 --> 00:55:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sam se sobom malo popričeš u ogledalu,

793
00:55:25,239 --> 00:55:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] to nije sramoča, to svi radimo manje više.

794
00:55:28,480 --> 00:55:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] Vidiš zašto si ljut, ko te tu u stvarnosti ljutiš,

795
00:55:30,760 --> 00:55:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] to te točno ne možeš to razumijet.

796
00:55:33,440 --> 00:55:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] I to je potpuno regla.

797
00:55:34,500 --> 00:55:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, recimo, ne mogu razumijet kvantnu fiziku,

798
00:55:37,239 --> 00:55:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala, nisam studirao uopće kak je.

799
00:55:39,380 --> 00:55:41,239
[SPEAKER_01] Prekomplicirano je za mene.

800
00:55:41,239 --> 00:55:43,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu shvatit ove dio medicine,

801
00:55:43,219 --> 00:55:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili nutricionizma,

802
00:55:45,659 --> 00:55:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne znam, kad sam vidio koliko je, recimo,

803
00:55:48,460 --> 00:55:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] znanost samo tijelovježba i znanost o pokretu, sportu,

804
00:55:53,320 --> 00:55:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] obogati.

805
00:55:54,780 --> 00:55:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ja samo to čitam, pametne ljude kojim Bogu hvala.

806
00:55:58,239 --> 00:55:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] To on či.

807
00:55:58,739 --> 00:55:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] Da, kak je.

808
00:55:59,659 --> 00:56:00,800
[SPEAKER_01] To on lipo je zaspal.

809
00:56:00,800 --> 00:56:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] On je djelovim.

810
00:56:01,599 --> 00:56:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] I uglavnom,

811
00:56:02,840 --> 00:56:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] i ona kažem,

812
00:56:04,320 --> 00:56:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] ok, pustimo to nekom drugome.

813
00:56:06,579 --> 00:56:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

814
00:56:07,139 --> 00:56:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Porazgovarati sam sa sobom,

815
00:56:09,420 --> 00:56:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] pokušati sam sebe popraviti,

816
00:56:10,860 --> 00:56:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne mogu tebe.

817
00:56:11,840 --> 00:56:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Uglavnom, evo,

818
00:56:13,139 --> 00:56:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način,

819
00:56:14,420 --> 00:56:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način komunicirati u budućnosti.

820
00:56:17,599 --> 00:56:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] Nekakav nadmeni sustav ne,

821
00:56:21,360 --> 00:56:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] iskreno govoriti da,

822
00:56:23,539 --> 00:56:26,860
[SPEAKER_01] i ja jako volim govoriti,

823
00:56:26,860 --> 00:56:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je ono što trenutno ne znamo.

824
00:56:29,900 --> 00:56:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer taj prostor, ne znam,

825
00:56:31,619 --> 00:56:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] je iskren i otvara.

826
00:56:33,260 --> 00:56:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] U medicini imaš koji svoj znanostelj svijeta,

827
00:56:36,239 --> 00:56:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] gomila prostora, ne znam.

828
00:56:38,059 --> 00:56:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

829
00:56:38,480 --> 00:56:40,300
[SPEAKER_01] I to je lijepo, a nije ružno,

830
00:56:40,300 --> 00:56:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer to nas goni prema naprijed.

831
00:56:41,940 --> 00:56:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] Biti iskren, komunikativan,

832
00:56:43,800 --> 00:56:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] i čuvat prirodu.

833
00:56:45,059 --> 00:56:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

834
00:56:45,380 --> 00:56:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, Sribor, hvala ti.

835
00:56:47,199 --> 00:56:47,800
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala tebi.

836
00:56:47,800 --> 00:56:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se dodemo na kavicu,

837
00:56:48,780 --> 00:56:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] tonac, dobro vidstvo želimo.

838
00:56:50,139 --> 00:56:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala svima koji ćete nas gledat.

839
00:56:53,260 --> 00:56:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, ekipa,

840
00:56:54,320 --> 00:56:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] do sljedećeg.

841
00:56:54,760 --> 00:56:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Čušpoj za bok.

842
00:56:55,579 --> 00:56:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pozdrav.

843
00:56:56,699 --> 00:56:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

844
00:56:59,900 --> 00:57:00,900
[UNKNOWN] Hvala.

